### Loading Project Secrets for Scrubbing

Query the `env_vars` table for secrets that should be redacted:

```typescript
private async loadProjectSecrets(): Promise<string[]> {
  const envVarRecords = await this.options.db
    .select({ value: envVars.value, isSecret: envVars.isSecret })
    .from(envVars)
    .where(
      and(
        eq(envVars.projectId, this.options.projectId),
        eq(envVars.isSecret, true),
      ),
    );

  // Decrypt the secret values (using the encryption module from shared)
  return envVarRecords.map((record) => decrypt(record.value));
}
```

